title: Teen Jessica Chambers burned alive, flammable liquid forced down her throat. Will there be justice?
itunes:title: Teen Jessica Chambers burned alive, flammable liquid forced down her throat. Will there be justice?
description:
Teen Jessica Chambers strangled and set on fire face. Two mistrials in this case so far. Will there be a third trial.The suspect in this case, Quinton Tellis, facing murder charges in another state. Will this case ever see justice?


Joining Nancy Grace today:

  • Darryl Cohen - Former Assistant District Attorney, Fulton County, Georgia, Defense Attorney 
  • Dr Bethany Marshall - Psychoanalyst, Beverly Hills, follow on instagram at DrBethanyMarshall
  • Steven Lampley - Former Detective - Author “Outside Your Door” www.stevenlampley.com
  • Dr. Kris Sperry - Retired Chief Medical Examiner State of Georgia
  • Michael Clark - WIAT CBS 42, Birmingham, Al Reporter

TIPLINE: (601) 948-5000
